@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.28) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.05)) + (wp.abs(v1 + 0.35) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.99)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.97 / v0 + 0.46)) + (0.50 / v2))
    v2 = v0
    tmp = (wp.exp(v2) * ((v2 + 0.78 + v0 + 0.67) - (v1 + 0.74 * tmp + 0.56)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs(0.93))
    v0 = (v2 * 0.37)
    data[tid] = v0
